<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko" class="bg-gray">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1">
    <title>BABATHE.COM - 나의 패션리더 정보</title>
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/library.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/common.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateA.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateB.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateC.css">
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="../../css/templateD.css">
    <script src="../../js/swiper-bundle.min.js"></script>
    <script src="../../js/layout.js"></script>
</head>
<body>
    <header>
        <div class="sub-hedaer">
            <button type="button" class="btn-back">뒤로가기</button>
            <h1 class="page-title">나의 패션리더 정보</h1>
            <button type="button" class="btn-search">검색</button>
            <button type="button" class="btn-cart">장바구니</button>
        </div>
    </header>
    <section>
        <div class="contentsGroup">
            <div class="metroUi gray2">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <strong>닉네임</strong>
                        <span>김바바</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>패션리더등급</strong>
                        <span>스페셜</span>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        <strong>활동기간</strong>
                        <span><em class="date">2020-12-01 ~</em> 현재 </span>
                    </li>
                </ul>
            </div>
            <h2>추천인 코드</h2>
            <li class="form-flex">
                <div class="form-flex-cell">
                    <input type="text" value="abcd123456" readonly class="align-c">
                </div>
                <div class="form-flex-btn">
                    <button class="btn-basicM">확인</button>
                </div>
            </li>
        </div>
        <div class="contentsGroup">
            <h2>활동 SNS 채널</h2>
            <div class="activeSnsChanel">
                <ul>
                    <li class="insta"><input type="text" placeholder="인스타 URL을 입력하지 않았습니다." required value="babathe"></li>
                    <li class="tiktok"><input type="text" placeholder="틱톡 URL을 입력하지 않았습니다." required value="babathe"></li>
                    <li class="youtube"><input type="text" placeholder="유투브 URL을 입력하지 않았습니다." required></li>
                    <li class="naver"><input type="text" placeholder="네이버 블로그 URL을 입력하지 않았습니다." required></li>
                    <li class="other"><input type="text" placeholder="기타 계정을 입력하지 않았습니다." required></li>
                </ul>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div class="contentsGroup">
            <h2>지원분야</h2>
            <div class="selectUI-circle">
                <div class="inner">
                    <label><input type="checkbox" name="select-1" checked><div><span class="thumb"><img src="http://placehold.it/200x200" alt=""></span><span class="txt">패션</span></div></label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" name="select-1"><div><span class="thumb"><img src="http://placehold.it/200x200" alt=""></span><span class="txt">뷰티</span></div></label>
                    <label><input type="checkbox" name="select-1" checked><div><span class="thumb"><img src="http://placehold.it/200x200" alt=""></span><span class="txt">헬스</span></div></label>
                </div>
                <div class="tipWrap">
                    <div class="tip type4">지원 분야 변경은 고객센터로 문의해 주세요.</div>
                </div>
            </div>
            <h2>신체사이즈</h2>
            <div class="bodySize">
                <h3>키</h3>
                <div class="form-flex">
                    <div class="form-flex-cell cm">
                        <input type="text" value="165" />
                        <span class="unit">CM</span>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3>상의</h3>
                <div class="optSelectWrap">
                    <div class="inner">
                        <label><input type="radio" name="optCheck-1"><span>44</span></label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="optCheck-1"><span>44</span></label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="optCheck-1" checked><span>55</span></label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="optCheck-1"><span>44</span></label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="optCheck-1"><span>44</span></label>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <h3>하의</h3>
                <div class="optSelectWrap">
                    <div class="inner">
                        <label><input type="radio" name="optCheck-2"><span>44</span></label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="optCheck-2" checked><span>44</span></label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="optCheck-2"><span>55</span></label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="optCheck-2"><span>44</span></label>
                        <label><input type="radio" name="optCheck-2"><span>44</span></label>
                    </div>
                </div>
            </div>

            <hr>

            <h2>사진</h2>
            <div class="attachedFileList onlyOne">
                <ul>
                    <li>
                        <input type="file" class="upload" title="이미지 업로드">
                        <div class="item">
                            <div class="thumb"><img src="http://placehold.it/146x146" alt=""></div>
                            <button class="del">삭제</button>
                        </div>
                    </li>
                </ul>
                <ol class="tip-wrap black">
                    <li>가장 자신을 잘 보여줄 수 있는 사진 1장을 첨부해주세요. <br>(파일명 : 바바패션리더_김바바)</li>
                    <li>10MB 이하 / 확장자 JPG, JPEG, PNG, GIF 파일</li>
                </ol>
            </div>

            <hr>
            
            <h2>자기소개</h2>

            <div class="event-write-wrap">
                <textarea cols="30" rows="9" placeholder="30대 직장인의 데일리 코디를 보여드립니다."></textarea>
                <p class="word-length">0 / 1000 자</p>
            </div>

            
            <div class="btnWrap">
                <button class="btn-basicL">정보 수정</button>
            </div>
        </div>
    </section>
    <footer></footer>
</body>
</html>